These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, spy
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, train
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | spy |
| Transport     | train | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, orange
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, golf
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | potato      | orange         |
| Sport   | cycling | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pumpkin
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | lemonade   |
| Food       | pumpkin  | avocado |

 #################################

 
